Description: Web portal for Raspberry Pi UPS node management
 Flask web portal for managing a UPS module on a Raspberry Pi node.
 Provides Wi-Fi management, UPS monitoring and load control
 via a mobile-friendly dark dashboard.
 .
 When the device cannot connect to a Wi-Fi network it raises
 a fallback hotspot so the user can configure networking via browser.
